enhanced_by.reason: The render method heavily relies on safelyAppend to write to the output stream, ensuring that the output is correctly formatted and error-handled.
The render method invokes listEndpoints to list different types of endpoints, ensuring that the endpoints are processed before other operations.
Both render and ol_changed methods handle the rendering of changes in the API, making ol_changed a good candidate for assertions related to the output format and content.
The ul_response method constructs a string representation of API responses, which can be used to verify the correctness of the response rendering in the render method.
